{"tid":1267502,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"部機開機兩秒就自動熄機無限loop","createTime":"2019-06-30T02:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T15:44:49.000Z","uid":11382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"823e843aa20dd3ba86852428cfd91cc88afcc5e1","tid":1267502,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:16:44.000Z","msg":"話說早兩日塊B85M打左柴，開機咩都唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後搵左塊二手B85M返黎試，初頭都開得返部機<br />\n到第二朝開機個陣就自己斷電，跟手又自己著返熄返<br />\n我試過拆RAM同拎板出黎就咁開，情況無改善<br />\n隻火牛試過無供電問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁係咪好大機會係塊二手板有事？"},{"pid":"ffbe079eb92e948325d4717dc49b6a324d7d6e05","tid":1267502,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:42:58.000Z","msg":"試第二條RAM"},{"pid":"dcea037a714acc43aca40db45719f89991081da4","tid":1267502,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffbe079eb92e948325d4717dc49b6a324d7d6e05","tid":1267502,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:42:58.000Z","msg":"試第二條RAM"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:51:44.000Z","msg":"試左，都係無限斷電reboot"},{"pid":"02a27d2493ee080329371da81fed3115c12c8dbc","tid":1267502,"uid":143394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:04:07.000Z","msg":"有機會係板既供電唔穩定 搞到咁<br />\ncheck清楚啲"},{"pid":"e91b27e51f55c97223accdec7d6f66b7c3b9bde2","tid":1267502,"uid":146893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:12:41.000Z","msg":"有機會塊老母板打柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9109148e3b99f958630e736e7f260e863e301f76","tid":1267502,"uid":127079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"823e843aa20dd3ba86852428cfd91cc88afcc5e1","tid":1267502,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:16:44.000Z","msg":"話說早兩日塊B85M打左柴，開機咩都唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後搵左塊二手B85M返黎試，初頭都開得返部機<br />\n到第二朝開機個陣就自己斷電，跟手又自己著返熄返<br />\n我試過拆RAM同拎板出黎就咁開，情況無改善<br />\n隻火牛試過無供電問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁係咪好大機會係塊二手板有事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"二手板，恭喜你可以買過塊"},{"pid":"e0268c8a117e1d7895ade90df4e2cc2ebdcbfbf1","tid":1267502,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"岩先同賣家傾，佢話尋日試係work既，最多換比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3291fe58d4d0bd45efad612437e473f6c599277","tid":1267502,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26a4edd72ed486bde1abb2e3eadaf4fa8f3d667","tid":1267502,"uid":167692,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:40:32.000Z","msg":"我個case應該唔關你事 不過照樣寫低<br />\n<br />\n我之前砌機都係試過咁兩秒自動熄機<br />\n但係因為個start button插支pin時唔啱方向 <br />\npin exposed metal touching the other pin's exposed metal part.<br />\n搞到自己short咗circuit<br />\n所以自動會熄機<br />\n擺到兩個pins唔touch鐵就ok"},{"pid":"2f9c0f7d4907d1b9e24373868629d2e4ce2d0406","tid":1267502,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"岩岩試左剩CPU+底板+火牛著機就唔會斷電<br />\n但無論插邊條Ram落去都會斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd6ad323cba4925b0325b7b212f7476fc55de15","tid":1267502,"uid":179672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:07:12.000Z","msg":"我開壞左粒5790k<br />\n有b85板要唔要<br />\n應該冇壞<br />\nB85 g1 b6"},{"pid":"052837e34b450ce0cf26fbacbfba15a312342a60","tid":1267502,"uid":179672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cd6ad323cba4925b0325b7b212f7476fc55de15","tid":1267502,"uid":179672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:07:12.000Z","msg":"我開壞左粒5790k<br />\n有b85板要唔要<br />\n應該冇壞<br />\nB85 g1 b6"},"cited